23
00:02:01,580 --> 00:02:02,370
She's the one.

24
00:02:04,370 --> 00:02:05,580
Sh-Shwen...

25
00:02:05,790 --> 00:02:06,870
Mr. Sheng,

26
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:09,250
