50
00:02:55,580 --> 00:02:56,580
A bet's a bet.

51
00:02:56,790 --> 00:02:59,580
What was your punishment again?

52
00:02:59,620 --> 00:03:00,580
Don't be so harsh.

53
00:03:00,620 --> 00:03:01,620
How about you

54
00:03:01,870 --> 00:03:03,700
treat everyone to coffee?

55
00:03:03,910 --> 00:03:04,910
Good job, everyone.

56
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:07,160
Ji Liunian's buying us all coffee.

57
00:03:21,540 --> 00:03:24,750
Hey, before Liunian gets back,

58
00:03:25,540 --> 00:03:26,870
should we sneak off?

59
00:03:28,160 --> 00:03:29,290
Where to?

60
00:03:30,660 --> 00:03:31,910
Not telling you.

61
00:03:36,370 --> 00:03:38,080
Just come with me.

62
00:03:46,470 --> 00:03:49,430
[Europark Ocean Kingdom]

63
00:03:56,370 --> 00:03:57,620
See?

64
00:03:58,120 --> 00:03:59,580
Told you I'd bring you somewhere fun.

65
00:03:59,700 --> 00:04:00,450
What do you think?

66
00:04:09,330 --> 00:04:10,700
We just took off like that,

67
00:04:11,200 --> 00:04:12,200
what about Liunian?

68
00:04:13,910 --> 00:04:15,620
Don't worry. Fanhua's there.

69
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:18,450
After all these years,

70
00:04:18,540 --> 00:04:19,910
