71
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:20,830
Yeah,

72
00:04:21,200 --> 00:04:22,870
Shengyao did sacrifice herself

73
00:04:22,910 --> 00:04:24,000
for him.

74
00:04:25,700 --> 00:04:26,450
Did you know

75
00:04:26,660 --> 00:04:29,200
Shengge has a thing for Fanhua?

76
00:04:29,500 --> 00:04:30,500
How do you know that?

77
00:04:30,620 --> 00:04:31,700
Whenever she calls me,

78
00:04:31,830 --> 00:04:34,040
she's always asking about him.

79
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:35,700
She's Shengyao's sister.

80
00:04:35,750 --> 00:04:36,750
Maybe if she came back

81
00:04:36,910 --> 00:04:38,200
and made a move,

82
00:04:38,500 --> 00:04:40,750
it could help him heal.

83
00:04:42,370 --> 00:04:43,750
Enough about that. Let's go.

84
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:48,160
If I could just be brave enough

85
00:04:48,250 --> 00:04:50,250
to apologize for what I did,

86
00:04:50,750 --> 00:04:52,910
would that heal your wounds too?

87
00:04:55,870 --> 00:04:57,500
Come on. What are you doing?

88
00:04:59,290 --> 00:05:00,580
Just looking at you.

89
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:14,140
♪With crayons, I draw a rainbow high♪

90
00:05:14,390 --> 00:05:18,270
♪Step by step, we reach the sky♪

91
00:05:18,520 --> 00:05:21,600
♪Courage is your way♪

92
00:05:22,220 --> 00:05:25,100
♪Proud of you every day♪

93
00:05:26,470 --> 00:05:30,140
♪One smile clears the sky♪

94
00:05:30,430 --> 00:05:34,310
♪Your laughter makes sadness fly♪

95
00:05:34,520 --> 00:05:37,810
♪Put down the horn of despair♪

96
00:05:38,140 --> 00:05:41,100
♪Let happiness take care♪

97
00:05:41,390 --> 00:05:45,770
♪Simply, no worries to bear♪

98
00:05:45,890 --> 00:05:49,310
♪That's the beauty of youth we share♪

99
00:05:49,640 --> 00:05:56,180
♪White smiles and fireworks flare♪

100
00:05:57,180 --> 00:06:00,180
♪You're my precious gift♪

101
00:06:00,220 --> 00:06:02,060
♪My whole life's shift♪

102
00:06:02,220 --> 00:06:05,890
♪I'll keep you close, no lie♪

103
00:06:06,220 --> 00:06:10,180
♪Love is like a spring breeze♪

104
00:06:10,270 --> 00:06:13,060
♪Warming all it sees♪

105
00:06:13,220 --> 00:06:15,970
♪You're my precious gift♪

106
00:06:16,140 --> 00:06:18,060
♪Happiness all the way♪

107
00:06:18,220 --> 00:06:21,140
♪Butterflies come out to play♪

108
00:06:21,430 --> 00:06:25,810
♪Together we reach our dreamland♪

109
00:06:26,100 --> 00:06:29,970
♪With sunshine in our hand♪

110
00:06:44,410 --> 00:06:46,120
So cute!

111
00:06:49,750 --> 00:06:51,370
It's been ages.

112
00:06:51,580 --> 00:06:52,290
Yeah.

113
00:06:52,410 --> 00:06:53,200
Remember?

114
00:06:53,250 --> 00:06:55,160
The four of us used to
come here all the time.

115
00:06:55,660 --> 00:06:56,500
And you...

116
00:07:12,020 --> 00:07:14,560
♪Memories hold tight♪

117
00:07:14,850 --> 00:07:18,020
♪Time ticks by in a trance♪

118
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:21,060
♪Time speeds away♪

119
00:07:21,060 --> 00:07:25,770
♪Fixing the cracks in our hands♪

120
00:07:26,310 --> 00:07:28,640
♪But I slowly turned away♪

121
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:32,000
En,

122
00:07:33,080 --> 00:07:33,620
I know things

123
00:07:33,750 --> 00:07:35,160
have been tough lately.

124
00:07:35,330 --> 00:07:36,500
I'm sorry for all the misunderstandings

125
00:07:36,660 --> 00:07:37,660
and hurt feelings.

126
00:07:38,950 --> 00:07:40,290
But my love for you

127
00:07:40,580 --> 00:07:41,580
has never changed.

128
00:07:42,290 --> 00:07:43,290
Do you believe me?

129
00:07:45,660 --> 00:07:47,000
I know I have

130
00:07:47,750 --> 00:07:49,790
made mistakes too.

131
00:07:49,790 --> 00:07:53,470
♪Tension rose, a brief chance♪

132
00:07:55,500 --> 00:07:56,950
Let's make today

133
00:07:57,250 --> 00:07:58,830
a fresh start.

134
00:07:59,950 --> 00:08:01,160
Just promise me

135
00:08:01,580 --> 00:08:03,120
you'll never lie to me again.

136
00:08:04,500 --> 00:08:05,500
I swear.

137
00:08:08,200 --> 00:08:08,950
Let's go.

138
00:08:08,950 --> 00:08:13,640
♪Letting you walk out of my play♪

139
00:08:14,500 --> 00:08:16,120
Look at all these fish!

140
00:08:21,700 --> 00:08:22,620
Shwenny,

141
00:08:22,910 --> 00:08:23,870
Shan.

142
00:08:24,790 --> 00:08:25,910
What are you guys doing here?

143
00:08:26,370 --> 00:08:27,370
I could ask you the same thing.

144
00:08:27,500 --> 00:08:29,410
Can you just stop showing up?

145
00:08:29,950 --> 00:08:30,700
Besides, is this place

146
00:08:30,750 --> 00:08:31,950
yours or something?

147
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:33,330
We can be wherever we want!

148
00:08:33,500 --> 00:08:34,870
En, Chengchi,

149
00:08:35,160 --> 00:08:36,330
what a pleasant surprise.

150
00:08:37,500 --> 00:08:38,870
I was just telling En how many memories

151
00:08:39,040 --> 00:08:40,370
we have from when we were kids.

152
00:08:40,580 --> 00:08:42,290
So many years have gone by.

153
00:08:42,950 --> 00:08:44,250
Let me make things straight,

154
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:46,330
when I said "gone",

155
00:08:46,500 --> 00:08:48,160
you meant it's in the past.

156
00:08:48,290 --> 00:08:49,700
No need to hold onto it.

157
00:08:49,910 --> 00:08:50,910
En, Chengchi,

158
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:52,580
we'll head out now.

159
00:08:53,660 --> 00:08:54,620
About last time,

160
00:08:54,910 --> 00:08:57,290
I'm sorry for misunderstanding you.

161
00:08:57,410 --> 00:08:58,660
Are we good?

162
00:08:59,370 --> 00:09:00,370
Of course, En.

163
00:09:00,500 --> 00:09:02,250
I was more worried
you'd be upset with me.

164
00:09:02,410 --> 00:09:03,500
We're family.

165
00:09:03,700 --> 00:09:04,950
No hard feelings.

166
00:09:05,200 --> 00:09:06,370
Exactly, no worries.

167
00:09:06,580 --> 00:09:07,450
We're family.

168
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:09,870
We're leaving.

169
00:09:09,950 --> 00:09:10,700
Let's go.

170
00:09:11,790 --> 00:09:12,830
Come on.

171
00:09:12,950 --> 00:09:13,950
Stop staring.

172
00:09:25,500 --> 00:09:27,910
I know you've always loved fireworks.

173
00:09:30,330 --> 00:09:32,700
You were never scared
of anything as a kid,

174
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:35,700
not even when I tried to
spook you with firecrackers.

175
00:09:35,910 --> 00:09:37,790
I used to wonder

176
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:40,500
what I could do to catch your attention.

177
00:09:40,910 --> 00:09:43,160
It became my biggest mission

178
00:09:43,500 --> 00:09:45,200
back then.

179
00:09:46,250 --> 00:09:48,080
You've got some nerve bringing that up.

180
00:09:49,620 --> 00:09:50,620
Chu,

181
00:09:50,950 --> 00:09:52,000
I'm sorry.

182
00:09:53,660 --> 00:09:55,660
Not just for messing with you
when we were kids,

183
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:57,200
but also for

184
00:09:57,410 --> 00:09:58,750
pushing you into marriage

185
00:09:58,910 --> 00:10:00,040
without asking.

186
00:10:00,540 --> 00:10:01,950
Can you forgive me?

187
00:10:17,040 --> 00:10:18,160
I already have.

188
00:10:18,410 --> 00:10:20,080
Look, look!

189
00:10:20,330 --> 00:10:21,370
A big one just went off.

190
00:10:25,500 --> 00:10:26,620
It's so beautiful.

191
00:10:26,850 --> 00:10:31,640
♪Your gentle smile lingers on my lips♪

192
00:10:31,930 --> 00:10:38,470
♪Engrave this beauty in my heart♪

193
00:10:38,850 --> 00:10:41,600
♪Every day from now♪

194
00:10:41,680 --> 00:10:46,270
♪In my memories, replaying it♪

195
00:10:49,100 --> 00:10:53,270
♪Replaying it♪

196
00:11:07,870 --> 00:11:08,870
Chengchi,

197
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:10,370
check out those fireworks.

198
00:11:10,660 --> 00:11:11,910
Aren't they stunning?

199
00:11:13,370 --> 00:11:14,250
Yes.

200
00:11:14,950 --> 00:11:16,250
But our future

201
00:11:16,500 --> 00:11:17,950
is going to be way better.

202
00:11:17,950 --> 00:11:23,430
♪Engrave this beauty in my heart♪

203
00:11:23,890 --> 00:11:26,600
♪Every day from now♪

204
00:11:26,640 --> 00:11:31,180
♪In my memories, replaying it♪

205
00:11:31,370 --> 00:11:32,450
You comfortable?

206
00:11:35,500 --> 00:11:36,540
Chu,

207
00:11:36,950 --> 00:11:37,870
let's make every day

208
00:11:37,950 --> 00:11:39,790
as happy as today, okay?

209
00:11:39,870 --> 00:11:40,750
Okay.

210
00:12:01,290 --> 00:12:02,120
Dad,

211
00:12:02,580 --> 00:12:03,750
it's time to cut our losses.

212
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:05,830
We can still pull out now.

213
00:12:09,200 --> 00:12:10,830
Here's the money I've saved up,

214
00:12:11,790 --> 00:12:12,700
plus the funds

215
00:12:12,790 --> 00:12:14,580
for the domestic branch.

216
00:12:15,700 --> 00:12:17,290
It should cover some of the losses.

217
00:12:18,120 --> 00:12:19,120
We'll figure out

218
00:12:19,660 --> 00:12:20,950
the rest.

219
00:12:25,500 --> 00:12:27,250
Are you Han Chuliang,

220
00:12:27,370 --> 00:12:28,910
the head of Han Investment?

221
00:12:29,370 --> 00:12:31,950
We suspect you of stock manipulation.

222
00:12:32,500 --> 00:12:34,660
[Arrest Warrant]
You'll need to come with us.

223
00:12:36,540 --> 00:12:37,910
My dad wouldn't do that!

224
00:12:38,080 --> 00:12:39,290
This has to be a mistake.

225
00:12:39,790 --> 00:12:40,910
Sir, please don't worry.

226
00:12:41,410 --> 00:12:43,080
We'll investigate thoroughly,

227
00:12:43,870 --> 00:12:44,500
but for now,

228
00:12:44,580 --> 00:12:46,040
please don't interfere.

229
00:12:47,500 --> 00:12:48,160
Dad,

230
00:12:48,330 --> 00:12:49,330
this is just a misunderstanding,

231
00:12:49,580 --> 00:12:50,540
right?

232
00:12:50,910 --> 00:12:52,200
You didn't do this.

233
00:12:53,120 --> 00:12:54,040
Dad.

234
00:12:54,540 --> 00:12:55,330
Dad!

235
00:13:04,040 --> 00:13:04,870
Mr. Sheng.

236
00:13:05,040 --> 00:13:05,910
What's going on?

237
00:13:06,040 --> 00:13:08,040
Director Han's been
manipulating our stocks.

238
00:13:08,160 --> 00:13:09,330
He's been taken in for questioning.

239
00:13:10,040 --> 00:13:12,000
Manipulating our stocks?

240
00:13:12,080 --> 00:13:13,000
Yes.

241
00:13:14,120 --> 00:13:15,120
Get me a report

242
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:16,240
on the recent stock movements.

243
00:13:16,540 --> 00:13:17,240
On it.

244
00:13:17,540 --> 00:13:19,410
Shwenny, what's happening?

245
00:13:24,700 --> 00:13:25,620
Han Chengchi,

246
00:13:26,120 --> 00:13:27,700
I just heard from the agent.

247
00:13:27,950 --> 00:13:29,410
You're canceling the lease
on Le Duo Building?

248
00:13:29,540 --> 00:13:30,370
Why?

249
00:13:31,040 --> 00:13:31,950
En,

250
00:13:33,120 --> 00:13:34,290
- I really...
- No matter what,

251
00:13:34,540 --> 00:13:35,040
you should have

252
00:13:35,120 --> 00:13:36,950
discussed this with me.

253
00:13:37,950 --> 00:13:38,870
Do you know how embarrassed I was

254
00:13:38,910 --> 00:13:39,790
when I found out

255
00:13:39,830 --> 00:13:41,160
from someone else?

256
00:13:41,660 --> 00:13:42,540
Didn't you promise yesterday

257
00:13:42,620 --> 00:13:43,910
you'd never lie to me?

258
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:45,540
And now this?

259
00:13:46,870 --> 00:13:47,870
I know.

260
00:13:48,410 --> 00:13:49,580
I'm sorry.

261
00:13:50,200 --> 00:13:52,240
But can we talk about this later?

262
00:13:53,990 --> 00:13:54,580
I've got

263
00:13:54,660 --> 00:13:55,870
something urgent to handle.

264
00:13:56,040 --> 00:13:57,990
What could be more important than this?

265
00:13:58,120 --> 00:13:59,080
Han Chengchi,

266
00:13:59,240 --> 00:14:00,740
you've really let me down!

267
00:14:13,120 --> 00:14:14,540
If you need help with anything,

268
00:14:14,620 --> 00:14:15,620
just ask.

269
00:14:15,950 --> 00:14:16,740
Thank you.

270
00:14:19,540 --> 00:14:20,330
Let's go.

271
00:14:24,450 --> 00:14:25,740
What exactly happened?

272
00:14:27,410 --> 00:14:29,540
Uncle Han's been caught faking reports

273
00:14:29,700 --> 00:14:30,870
and inflating stock prices.

274
00:14:31,660 --> 00:14:34,620
Why would he do that out of the blue?

275
00:14:40,080 --> 00:14:41,080
Mr. Sheng,

276
00:14:41,450 --> 00:14:43,120
these officers are from
the Securities Regulatory Commission.

277
00:14:44,620 --> 00:14:46,410
Are you Sheng Group's CEO, Sheng Shi?

278
00:14:46,830 --> 00:14:47,370
Yes.

279
00:14:47,450 --> 00:14:48,580
We suspect you're involved

280
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:50,160
in the stock manipulation case

281
00:14:50,240 --> 00:14:51,700
with Han Group.

282
00:14:51,830 --> 00:14:54,120
You'll need to come with us.

283
00:15:16,890 --> 00:15:17,350
Hello?

284
00:15:17,600 --> 00:15:17,950
Hey,

285
00:15:17,950 --> 00:15:18,990
Lanshan, bad news!

286
00:15:19,160 --> 00:15:20,790
Shwenny's been taken in
by the Securities Regulatory Commission.

287
00:15:20,870 --> 00:15:21,740
What?

288
00:15:22,220 --> 00:15:25,680
[China Securities Regulatory Commission,
Fujian Branch]

289
00:15:25,950 --> 00:15:28,330
If the shareholders find out,

